channel.name: BBC One NL
channel.title: Live: WA World Athletics Championships
channel.desc: The action on day five of the World Athletics Championships reaches its conclusion, and after springing a surprise to win gold in Budapest two years ago, Great Britain's Josh Kerr is back to defend his 1500m title. It won't be easy with competition coming from a strong American contingent and Norway's Jakob Ingebrigtsen, if he can prove his fitness.
